Program to communicate between processes ( server and client ) using fifo IPC.

create.c : Program to create a file server and client using mkfifo
server.c : Read the request from the client and replied back to client
client.c : Display message into terminal which replied by the server

Approach :
  1) Create a fifo server and client using mkfifo system call (./create)
  2) Communicate between the processes (server and client)

Procedure to run the code
1) make 
2) ./create
2) ./server
3) ./client
